<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
      margin: 40px auto;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
        Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif,
        Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    "
  >
    <table
      align="center"
      width="100%"
      role="presentation"
      cellspacing="0"
      cellpadding="0"
      border="0"
      style="
        max-width: 100%;
        border-width: 1px;
        border-style: solid;
        box-shadow: 0 0 #0000, 0 0 #0000, 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
          0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 0.25rem;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        width: 550px;
        border-color: rgb(102, 126, 234);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      "
    >
      <tbody>
        <tr style="width: 100%">
          <td>
            <!-- Background Gradient Effect -->
            <table
              align="center"
              width="100%"
              border="0"
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
              style="
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                right: 0;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 0;
                pointer-events: none;
              "
            >
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td
                    style="
                      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1) 0%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.1) 100%);
                      filter: blur(40px);
                    "
                  ></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- Logo Section -->
            <table
              align="center"
              width="100%"
              border="0"
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
              style="margin-top: 32px"
            >
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td style="text-align: center">
                    <div
                      style="
                        display: inline-block;
                        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
                        width: 4rem;
                        height: 4rem;
                        border-radius: 1rem;
                        line-height: 4rem;
                        margin: 0 auto;
                      "
                    >
                      <span
                        style="
                          color: white;
                          font-size: 24px;
                          font-weight: 700;
                          letter-spacing: 2px;
                        "
                        >Z</span
                      >
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- Title -->
            <h1
              style="
                color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
                font-size: 18px;
                font-weight: 400;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 30px 0;
              "
            >
              欢迎加入 <strong>Zeta</strong>！
            </h1>

            <!-- Greeting -->
            <p
              style="
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin: 16px 0;
                color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
              "
            >
              您好，<strong><%= name %></strong>！
            </p>

            <p
              style="
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin: 16px 0;
                color: rgb(51, 51, 51);
              "
            >
              感谢您注册 Zeta 平台。请点击下方按钮验证您的邮箱地址：
            </p>

            <!-- CTA Button -->
            <table
              align="center"
              width="100%"
              border="0"
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
              style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0"
            >
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <a
                      href="<%= verificationUrl %>"
                      target="_blank"
                      style="
                        line-height: 100%;
                        text-decoration: none;
                        display: inline-block;
                        max-width: 100%;
                        padding: 12px 32px;
                        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
                        border-radius: 0.25rem;
                        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
                        font-size: 14px;
                        font-weight: 600;
                        text-align: center;
                      "
                      >验证邮箱</a
                    >
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- Verification Link Box -->
            <table
              align="center"
              width="100%"
              border="0"
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
              style="
                background-color: rgb(243, 244, 246);
                border-radius: 0.75rem;
                padding: 1rem;
                margin: 16px 0;
              "
            >
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p
                      style="
                        font-size: 12px;
                        line-height: 20px;
                        margin: 0;
                        color: rgb(107, 114, 128);
                      "
                    >
                      验证链接：
                    </p>
                    <p
                      style="
                        font-size: 13px;
                        line-height: 20px;
                        margin: 8px 0 0 0;
                        color: rgb(51, 51, 51);
                        word-break: break-all;
                      "
                    >
                      <%= verificationUrl %>
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <hr
              style="
                width: 100%;
                border: none;
                border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
                margin: 26px 0;
              "
            />

            <!-- Quote -->
            <table
              align="center"
              width="100%"
              border="0"
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
            >
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p
                      style="
                        font-size: 12px;
                        line-height: 24px;
                        margin: 16px 0;
                        color: rgb(107, 114, 128);
                        text-align: center;
                      "
                    >
                      "The only way to do great work is to love what you do."
                      <br />— Steve Jobs
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <table
              align="center"
              width="100%"
              border="0"
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
              style="margin-top: 1rem"
            >
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p
                      style="
                        font-size: 11px;
                        line-height: 20px;
                        margin: 16px 0;
                        text-align: center;
                        color: rgb(156, 163, 175);
                      "
                    >
                      此链接将在24小时后失效。<br />
                      如果您没有注册 Zeta 账号，请忽略此邮件。<br />
                      本邮件为系统自动发送，请勿直接回复。<br />
                      © <%= year %> Zeta. All rights reserved.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
